# graphify — ignore machine-local internals (cache/, manifest.json, absolute-path
# caches, cost tracker, temp .graphify_* files) AND the large generated artifacts
# graph.json (~3MB) + graph.html, which the post-commit/post-checkout hooks rebuild
# on every commit and otherwise churn ~90k lines in every diff. They stay on disk
# locally (queries still work) and a fresh clone regenerates them via the hooks /
# `graphify .`. Only the human-readable GRAPH_REPORT.md is committed to share.
graphify-out/*
!graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md

# git worktrees (superpowers using-git-worktrees skill)
/.worktrees/

# Playwright E2E artifacts
/tests/e2e/.auth/
/tests/e2e/.report/
/tests/e2e/.artifacts/
/playwright-report/
/test-results/
/tests/e2e/.env.e2e
/tests/prod-smoke/.artifacts/
